               <h1><em>Quark</em></h1>
               <h4>Evolving product landing page template</h4>
               <p>Quark for Joomla 3 is not just an original template that works as a superb product promotion platform; it's also constantly evolving with new features, pages and styles to meet a diverse range of needs.</p>
               <p>Stun your visitors with remarkable visuals, including a parallax-effect packed frontpage that frames your content beautifully, image sliders that blend naturally for a subtle, enticing effect, and reveal and other CSS3 powered animations for that extra touch of magic.</p>
               <p>On the features side of things you have all you need to deliver premium content, with pre-prepared huge video blocks, tabbed areas that can display a huge range of modules, and a massive selection of HTML benefits like price tables, team, blog, under construction and contact pages.</p> 
